    <p>
      I'm a platform / SRE engineer focused on running real systems well:
      GitOps-driven Kubernetes, self-hosted CI/CD, and observability that
      actually catches things. The homelab behind this page is where I prove
      those ideas out end to end.
    </p>

    <h2>What this site is</h2>
    <p>
      A single static Go binary that embeds this front-end and serves a small
      live API. It reads cluster metrics from VictoriaMetrics and recent commits
      from Gitea over the cluster-internal network, exposes its own Prometheus
      metrics, and is deployed by the same ArgoCD pipeline as every other
      service — so it monitors the platform that runs it.
    </p>

